PixelPipe is an open source, cross platform 3D graphics software pipeline 
written in C++. The software pipeline includes programmable fragment and 
vertex shader stages. External textures can be loaded using JPGs, PNGs,
or TIFF files.


BUILDING THE SOFTWARE 
===============================================================================
This software relies on CMake for building. If you don't have it installed 
please visit cmake.org first.

Linux/Unix/OSX
-----------------------------------------------------------


Windows
-----------------------------------------------------------
Windows is not yet formally supported. 



